<div class=3D"row">
<div class=3D"col-12 col-md-9">
<div class=3D"post__byline post__author vcard">
<p>By <a href=3D"https://www.ncsa.illinois.edu/author/ahelreg2/" rel=3D"aut=
hor" class=3D"fn">
Andrew Helregel
</a></p>
</div>
<div class=3D"post__content">
<p>Participants of NCSA=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"http://spin.ncsa.illinois.edu/=
" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">Students Pushing Innovation=
 (SPIN) program</a> gained notoriety for their many accomplishments over th=
e 2021-22 academic year.</p>
<p>Among them were returning interns <a href=3D"http://spin.ncsa.illinois.e=
du/interns/#hconnors" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">Haihley=
 Connors</a>, <a href=3D"http://spin.ncsa.illinois.edu/interns/#herzig" tar=
get=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">Quentin Herzig</a> and <a href=
=3D"http://spin.ncsa.illinois.edu/interns/#hluo" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"n=
oreferrer noopener">Haolin Luo</a>, recipients of the 2021 Jerry Fiddler In=
novation Undergraduate Fellowship award. These three students were among th=
e <a href=3D"https://www.ncsa.illinois.edu/ncsa-awards-20-fiddler-innovatio=
n-fellowships-to-illinois-students-and-faculty/">20 awardees</a> who were r=
ecognized at a virtual ceremony in November for their exceptional contribut=
ions to interdisciplinary research projects that explore new topics and inn=
ovation.</p>
<div class=3D"wp-block-image">
<figure class=3D"alignleft size-medium is-resized"><img decoding=3D"async" =
src=3D"https://www.ncsa.illinois.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/hconnors-1-=
300x300.png" alt=3D"" class=3D"wp-image-8369" width=3D"220" height=3D"220">=
<figcaption>Portrait of Haihley Connors.</figcaption></figure></div>
<p>=E2=80=9CI am extremely honored to be nominated and to receive the 2021 =
Jerry Fiddler Innovation Undergraduate Fellowship award,=E2=80=9D Connors s=
aid. =E2=80=9CAfter hearing about the prestige of this award, I felt so ble=
ssed to be a recipient. Mr. Fiddler=E2=80=99s accomplishments are utterly a=
mazing, and this recognition has pushed me to work even harder.=E2=80=9D</p=
>
<p>Connors and Herzig credited the network of researchers, faculty and staf=
f in their achievements.</p>
<p>=E2=80=9CThe connections and opportunities the NCSA provides us interns =
with are once in a lifetime, and I am so grateful to be a part of the progr=
am,=E2=80=9D Connors said.</p>
<div class=3D"wp-block-image">
<figure class=3D"alignright size-full is-resized"><img decoding=3D"async" s=
rc=3D"https://www.ncsa.illinois.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RSED051622-S=
